damage to enemies directly ahead,<br>inflicts bleeding, and grants the entire team<br>a team strength amp.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Damage: 1,800 \\u00d7 1 hit<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbBleeding<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 30 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 4.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Damage: 146<br>Team Amps:<br>\\u30fbTeam Strength Amp (MAX Lv. = 2)<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span><span>(Water) Strength +70%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Water: <br>increases strength by 70%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/2d1c0915b797937c5ea76997544d95672.png\\"><\/span><span>(Water) Wyrm of War II<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Water:<br>fills 100% of skill gauges at the start of quests,<br>and increases attack skill damage by 40% when<br>the user has a team strength amp.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbThe stats shown here represent the dragon at maximum level, maximum bond, and fully unbound. They do not represent the stats when first obtained.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.<\/div><div>2. Alberian Battle Royale skins for adventurers featured in this summon showcase will go on sale, and it will cost fewer items to unlock their skins. Note that some adventurers do not have adventurer skins.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1626242400,"prev_article_id":"2293","next_article_id":"2294","image_path":"","update_time":1626252029}}}'